《'''公报'''》（{{lang-fr|La Gazette}}），初名《'''法国公报'''》（Gazette de France<ref name="李谷城2000">{{cite book|author=李谷城|title=香港报业百年沧桑|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DYV9AAAAIAAJ|year=2000|publisher=明报出版社|isbn=978-962-973-451-0|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001022039/https://books.google.com/books?id=DYV9AAAAIAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>），是[[法国|法国]]出版的第一份[[周刊|周刊]]<ref name="PAPADOPOULOS2018">{{cite book|author=Maria PAPADOPOULOS|title=Spartan Kings and Statesmen in Montaigne's Essais: Sparta, a city-state of philosophers|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=3--EDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA76|date=2018-12-24|publisher=Méduse d'Or S.A.R.L.|isbn=978-2-900409-00-8|pages=76–|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923013656/https://books.google.com/books?id=3--EDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA76|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是法国历史最悠久的报纸<ref>{{cite book|title=Marketing Communications|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-6c9AQAAMAAJ|year=1900|pages=18–|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120054435/https://books.google.com/books?id=-6c9AQAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由[[泰奥夫拉斯特·勒诺多|泰奥夫拉斯特·勒诺多]]（Théophraste Renaudot）创办<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/books/features/rowling-finally-confirms-how-to-pronounce-hermiones-name/articleshow/65909703.cms|title=JK Rowling finally confirms how to pronounce Hermione's name|date=2018-09-21|publisher=[[Times_of_India|Times of India]]|accessdate=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703144417/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/books/features/rowling-finally-confirms-how-to-pronounce-hermiones-name/articleshow/65909703.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>，第一版于1631年5月30日发行<ref name="Walravens2008">{{cite book|author=Hartmut Walravens|title=International Newspaper Librarianship for the 21st Century|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=g3-LvEMFlYkC&pg=PA235|date=2008-12-19|publisher=Walter de Gruyter|isbn=978-3-598-44020-5|pages=235–|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801202054/https://books.google.com/books?id=g3-LvEMFlYkC&pg=PA235|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它逐渐成为法国[[保皇派|保皇派]]（royalist）之一——[[正统派_(法国政党)|正统派]]（legitimists<ref>{{cite book|author1=罗伯特·图姆斯|author2=伊莎贝尔·图姆斯|title=甜蜜的世仇|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=G57qDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT120|date=2019年12月3日|publisher=卫城出版|isbn=978-986-97165-9-8|pages=120–|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201004025411/https://books.google.com/books?id=G57qDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT120|dead-url=no}}</ref>）的喉舌（mouthpiece）<ref name=Ory>Pascal Ory, "La nouvelle droite fin de siècle" in Nouvelle histoire des idées politiques (dir. P. Ory), Hachette Pluriel 1987, pp.457-465</ref>。

20世纪初，随着法国[[现代|现代]][[新闻媒体|新闻媒体]]的兴起和全国各地专业化、地方化报纸的出现，该报于在1915年停刊<ref name="McCabe2008">{{cite book|author=Ina Baghdiantz McCabe|title=Orientalism in Early Modern France: Eurasian Trade, Exoticism and the Ancien Regime|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=WWatAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA368|date=2008-07-15|publisher=Berg|isbn=978-1-84520-374-0|pages=368–|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715210626/https://books.google.com/books?id=WWatAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA368|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

